01:20:25.186 --> 01:20:26.881
I'll be so lonely.

01:20:39.033 --> 01:20:40.398
Oh, Mama...

01:20:43.304 --> 01:20:44.669
I love you.

01:22:04.285 --> 01:22:05.616
Rachel.

01:22:18.299 --> 01:22:21.268
Wait! Wait for me!
